ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6efb3ebb304bd20a41313d134a86aa936f9770","tid":1691873,"uid":18728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:17:47.000Z","msg":"同意社會必須長遠擁黃制藍, 罷買罷食藍店係一種長期抗爭, 如果有二百萬人一齊長期堅持落去係好有用<br />\n可惜港豬真係太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63cd4a3d2fa8b9d8cb8d9fd6aa13f14518183d38","tid":1691873,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:21:04.000Z","msg":"和勇合作 長期抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053876fd66aab247e550035a0742bd37b63049a3","tid":1691873,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:21:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「要記住：輸咩都可以接受，就係唔可以輸自己」。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12cc87720cc1c984710949efaec90dc6400c02c2","tid":1691873,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b6efb3ebb304bd20a41313d134a86aa936f9770","tid":1691873,"uid":18728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:17:47.000Z","msg":"同意社會必須長遠擁黃制藍, 罷買罷食藍店係一種長期抗爭, 如果有二百萬人一齊長期堅持落去係好有用<br />\n可惜港豬真係太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:22:52.000Z","msg":"唔好咁灰 身邊好多和理已好盡力 罷買罷食藍店同支持黃店日日做文宣 遊說淺藍既朋友轉黃<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95fa934a15b17869e1fa1412bd78e0b188c5122","tid":1691873,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfb20b05e916d5fe00a7cff7ec1d12b17fe9c3c2","tid":1691873,"uid":30247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy"